Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.95,0:00:22.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這一天又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.17,0:00:29.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這究竟是第幾次了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.23,0:02:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.23,0:02:05.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(919,589)}「永遠不會被追上的是？」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.65,0:02:05.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成立紀念典禮盛況落幕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.82,0:02:08.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們黑組的戲劇也獲得了大大的成功
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.78,0:02:11.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老師我最後哭的是稀里嘩啦的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.16,0:02:16.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 桐谷樞 生田目千足 劍持詩繪那
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.66,0:02:20.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又突然有三個人轉校了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.83,0:02:22.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是各位 打起精神來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.13,0:02:25.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老師也和你們一樣寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.80,0:02:29.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的7個人 一起努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.68,0:02:36.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溝呂木老師 和平時一樣 真有活力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.06,0:02:40.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然這麼遲鈍 真是讓人火大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.98,0:02:46.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是因為他的那種性格 才被選作黑組班主任的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.57,0:02:49.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的 兔角同學
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.49,0:02:53.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按照老師說的努力下去 一定會開創未來的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.37,0:02:55.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無用的積極性啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.58,0:02:58.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真想壓斷你的鼻子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.00,0:03:01.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭 好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.83,0:03:03.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了好了 你們幾個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.13,0:03:05.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要白費力氣去爭辯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.13,0:03:10.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起那個 現在要不要休息一下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.63,0:03:12.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休息？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.51,0:03:14.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.64,0:03:16.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我找到了一個有趣的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.81,0:03:19.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放學後 大家一起去看看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.73,0:03:28.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是明星學園
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.19,0:03:30.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然連這種東西都有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.15,0:03:34.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教學使用的泳池在別的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.91,0:03:38.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我拜託老師 讓它成為黑組的包場了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.87,0:03:41.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家盡情的享受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.12,0:03:44.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泳衣也準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.83,0:03:46.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你 首藤同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.96,0:03:49.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兔角同學 快點換衣服游泳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.01,0:03:51.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.42,0:03:52.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一之瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.55,0:03:56.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 我們也去換衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.72,0:04:02.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,校園泳衣…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.85,0:04:05.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,準備的泳衣就是這種嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.60,0:04:06.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太土了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.94,0:04:09.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種如花似玉的大好年紀能穿這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.65,0:04:11.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是不想穿學校指定的泳衣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.11,0:04:14.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有各種各樣的泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.45,0:04:16.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以挑自己喜歡的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.53,0:04:19.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鳰同學 你打算潛水嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.37,0:04:22.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是拘束服風格
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.04,0:04:25.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼我選這個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.58,0:04:28.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晴想穿這種普通的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.17,0:04:30.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兔角同學呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.63,0:04:34.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 真是大膽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.84,0:04:36.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定會走光
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.01,0:04:40.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,東同學有走光的本錢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.39,0:04:45.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太暴露了 危難關頭無法保護身體
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.56,0:04:50.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利於行動的運動泳衣是明智之選
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.98,0:04:54.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}遊戲開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.19,0:04:54.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遊戲？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.11,0:04:57.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.62,0:04:59.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要慌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.99,0:05:02.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是想硬扯下來 會爆炸的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.83,0:05:03.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炸彈？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.00,0:05:04.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.33,0:05:06.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然火力很弱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.83,0:05:09.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是從裝在脖子上的狀態爆炸的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.79,0:05:11.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毫無疑問會即刻死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.80,0:05:14.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我對武力可沒有什麼自信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.55,0:05:16.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是要通過遊戲一決勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.43,0:05:20.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炸彈的時限是今晚零點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.51,0:05:22.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是在那之前沒能解除的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.68,0:05:24.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是我贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.35,0:05:26.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.64,0:05:29.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是殺了我 也無法避免爆炸哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.98,0:05:32.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解除起爆裝置的方法只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.48,0:05:36.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有輸入4位密碼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.36,0:05:40.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 只能嘗試3次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.03,0:05:44.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是輸錯3次 咚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.87,0:05:46.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴我密碼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.66,0:05:49.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遊戲就是要找到它
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.17,0:05:53.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和密碼的數字一樣的四張牌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.25,0:05:55.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藏在了這個泳池設施裏面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.88,0:05:58.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到的話 就會知道4個數字
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.84,0:06:00.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隱藏地點的提示 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.93,0:06:02.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和予告票放在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.72,0:06:05.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一張在森林中最適合隱藏的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.60,0:06:07.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一張在水中 要用重要的東西交換
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.56,0:06:09.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一張在黑暗中 聲音會指引你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.56,0:06:11.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一張在光明中 在耀眼到看不見之前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.44,0:06:15.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能解開這個謎團嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.78,0:06:19.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧 大家一起享受遊戲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.24,0:06:22.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事 別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.41,0:06:25.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定會解除起爆裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.12,0:06:27.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兔角同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.33,0:06:29.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一張在森林中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.71,0:06:31.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個是森林？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.08,0:06:34.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能被這樣叫的只有那裏了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.75,0:06:36.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一張在水中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.13,0:06:39.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是說在泳池裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.63,0:06:41.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,項圈是防水的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.80,0:06:43.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跳進水裏也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.51,0:06:50.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不過爆炸的時候 就算在水裏也會爆炸哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.90,0:06:57.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本來就是說什麼予告票 搞得像遊戲一樣的暗殺規則
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.15,0:07:00.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次真的就是遊戲？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.95,0:07:04.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正也厭倦了只有血腥的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.41,0:07:06.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶爾像這樣也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.08,0:07:11.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說黑組的主辦人真的打算殺死晴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.92,0:07:13.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道什麼的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.25,0:07:16.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰知道呢 是怎麼回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.55,0:07:20.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實是想試試什麼的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.18,0:07:23.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們真正的目的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.05,0:07:26.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起那個 乖乖看著好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.68,0:07:31.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是小晴就這樣死了 遊戲就要就此結束了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.14,0:07:33.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是這樣就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.73,0:07:37.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說明這不過是這種程度的遊戲而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.03,0:07:41.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們就先在這裏圍觀了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.40,0:07:44.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的話 番場同學也請嘗嘗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.62,0:07:47.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.45,0:07:50.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不錯啊 就像是休養地一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.62,0:07:53.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也無憂無慮的打西瓜如何
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.79,0:07:57.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正好這裏放了不錯的西瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.75,0:07:58.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.17,0:08:01.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暗殺者對抗打西瓜？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.80,0:08:04.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼武器都行 可以這樣理解嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.35,0:08:09.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 那個很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.43,0:08:12.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說 你打算蒙著眼睛射擊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.82,0:08:20.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.61,0:08:23.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再往右一點 啊過了 再往左一點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.61,0:08:27.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算不這麼告訴我 也會百發百中的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.16,0:08:31.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個不叫打西瓜 叫西瓜粉碎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.12,0:08:35.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 兔角同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.33,0:08:39.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一張在黑暗中 聲音會指引你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.30,0:08:41.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是指打西瓜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.64,0:08:53.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到一張了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.60,0:08:56.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,方片7
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.56,0:09:00.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦哦 真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.48,0:09:02.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真厲害 不愧是兔角同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.36,0:09:09.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我的話 會更簡單的同時找到4張哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.49,0:09:12.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的3張你也知道了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.00,0:09:14.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.50,0:09:16.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡單得不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.12,0:09:18.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撲克牌 剩餘
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.29,0:09:22.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 番場同學也明白了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.30,0:09:23.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.92,0:09:25.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撲克牌 剩餘？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.80,0:09:29.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 你注意到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.51,0:09:33.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是從這裏拿走了4張牌的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.39,0:09:35.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算不用找到剩餘的4張
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.64,0:09:39.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要看看少了哪張牌 就能知道4個數字是什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.35,0:09:41.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此 逆向思維
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.28,0:09:46.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,4張7
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.95,0:09:49.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,密碼是7777嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.82,0:09:55.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是位列最不能作為密碼使用的數字前三的組合嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.08,0:10:01.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 該怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.25,0:10:03.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晴 過來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.93,0:10:13.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.82,0:10:27.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真遺憾那
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.15,0:10:31.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那副撲克從一開始就是用作幌子的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.41,0:10:34.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浪費了寶貴的一次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.74,0:10:37.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣 能夠嘗試的就只剩2次了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.79,0:10:40.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.59,0:10:50.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了不再出現轉校生 要在關心學生上做到萬無一失
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.18,0:10:55.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一之瀨和東沒有家人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.31,0:11:00.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在她們面前避免談論溫暖的家庭話題比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.31,0:11:04.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.86,0:11:16.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs35}不老癥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.86,0:11:16.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs35}國內外這種病例都是少之又少
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.86,0:11:16.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs35}關於這個病情有很多不明之處
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.86,0:11:16.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs35}雖然被認為是\N與細胞自我死亡\N相關的遺傳基因的異常
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.86,0:11:16.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs35}卻尚未被解釋清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.86,0:11:16.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs35}治療方法也沒有確立
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.20,0:11:19.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太陽已經下山了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.33,0:11:21.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.67,0:11:24.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多該我出場了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.42,0:11:26.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你出來也無事可做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.96,0:11:28.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說你這個性格穿校園泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.92,0:11:30.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超級不適合你的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.30,0:11:35.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你給我閉嘴 穿校園泳衣游泳是真晝的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.60,0:11:36.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,游泳去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.10,0:11:43.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還特意準備了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.06,0:11:44.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是有精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.69,0:11:48.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距時限0點 還有的是時間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.15,0:11:51.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家也再多享受享受
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.49,0:11:53.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夜場照明也非常完備
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.41,0:12:00.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在光明中 在耀眼到看不見之前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.54,0:12:04.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那裏面的某個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.25,0:12:06.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兔角同學 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.72,0:12:19.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二張
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.31,0:12:22.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,joker？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.56,0:12:24.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我忘記說了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.27,0:12:26.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,joker是數字0的替代
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.94,0:12:31.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,7和0
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.32,0:12:34.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很順利呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.57,0:12:36.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還剩下兩張
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.30,0:12:59.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一張在森林中最適合隱藏的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.68,0:13:03.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一張在水中 要用重要的東西交換
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.52,0:13:08.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下就是森林中和水中了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.69,0:13:10.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼最適合啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.98,0:13:14.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家常說葉隱於林對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.69,0:13:19.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 但是現在找的是撲克牌 不是樹葉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.28,0:13:22.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兔角同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.50,0:13:27.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 那副牌你剛才看過了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.00,0:13:29.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我告訴你它是假的了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.34,0:13:34.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.09,0:13:39.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑桃A
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.59,0:13:43.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真厲害 剩下的一張在水中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.39,0:13:46.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要用重要的東西交換
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.44,0:13:48.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重要的東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.27,0:13:52.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一之瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.23,0:13:55.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 爆炸了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.78,0:13:59.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生日快樂 首藤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.49,0:14:00.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生日？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.82,0:14:02.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你為什麼不說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.74,0:14:05.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是告訴我的話 我還能準備點什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.87,0:14:10.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之 現在我能做的 只有這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.08,0:14:13.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老師 這裏是禁止男生進入的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.01,0:14:18.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭 說什麼生日 其實是來偷窺的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.88,0:14:20.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是年少氣盛啊 老師
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.22,0:14:23.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 你們在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.97,0:14:25.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 快點給我消失
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.31,0:14:27.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這個工口教師
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.10,0:14:29.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,番場 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.85,0:14:31.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說話這麼粗魯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.36,0:14:35.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等 等一下 老師只是想和大家一起慶祝首藤的生日…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.98,0:14:38.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是生日啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.57,0:14:39.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.78,0:14:41.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.24,0:14:46.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是暗殺成功的話 那個報酬正好可以當做禮物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.16,0:14:49.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正是想要這個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.25,0:14:50.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首藤同學的報酬是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.12,0:14:52.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還沒確認過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.79,0:14:55.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的願望是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.38,0:14:58.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普通的變老 死去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.72,0:15:02.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.47,0:15:07.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的身體生病了 「肉體不會變老」的病
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.27,0:15:12.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽說過 好像是叫不老癥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.77,0:15:16.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都能永葆青春 不是很棒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.15,0:15:18.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的這麼認為嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.99,0:15:23.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有自己不會老
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.16,0:15:25.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都棄我而去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.78,0:15:28.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾經也有過重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.41,0:15:33.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個人比我還要小一歲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.54,0:15:35.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且生日只差一天
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.80,0:15:41.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在他趕上我的年紀之前 我又長了一歲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.55,0:15:45.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永遠都不會變成同一個年紀呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.72,0:15:47.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們還曾這樣笑談過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.43,0:15:51.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 不管怎麼年紀如何增長
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.35,0:15:53.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也絲毫不曾改變
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.85,0:15:57.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有那個人超過了我 變成了大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.86,0:16:02.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而最終 那個人從我面前離開了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.24,0:16:11.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此 我的願望是普通的變老 死去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.46,0:16:13.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.83,0:16:17.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會從全世界搜集最棒的醫生成立小組
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.63,0:16:19.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,探索治療方法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.17,0:16:21.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.92,0:16:22.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首藤同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.35,0:16:28.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只剩下很少嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.14,0:16:32.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在磨蹭什麼 東兔角
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.27,0:16:35.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一個謎題
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.15,0:16:40.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不快點回答我的話 會被別人搶先的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.58,0:16:53.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一張在水中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.17,0:16:55.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.79,0:16:58.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.05,0:17:02.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.34,0:17:05.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這也是水中？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.93,0:17:07.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是水
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.05,0:17:10.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快到時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.51,0:17:12.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小晴要在我眼前爆炸了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.18,0:17:17.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水中 用重要的東西交換？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.65,0:17:18.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.65,0:17:24.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是盲點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.03,0:17:27.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個管子中也流著水
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.93,0:17:48.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兔角同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.76,0:17:50.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.65,0:17:59.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.85,0:18:00.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡鑰匙？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.82,0:18:02.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用這個開嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.36,0:18:05.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第4張牌？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.95,0:18:14.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一張在水中 要用重要的東西交換
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.83,0:18:16.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用這個就會得救了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.66,0:18:18.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但卻會失去牌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.33,0:18:22.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是讓我為了一之瀨去死嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.05,0:18:26.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一之瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.84,0:18:29.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是第4張卡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.65,0:18:49.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的 不行 一之瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.21,0:19:09.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兔角同學 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.26,0:19:10.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.22,0:19:12.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 失去了最後的牌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.18,0:19:13.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.72,0:19:18.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了3個數字
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.77,0:19:20.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,7 0 1
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.39,0:19:23.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的一個 只能推測了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.19,0:19:29.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,推測能夠知道該用什麼樣的組合輸入嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.03,0:19:31.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交給伊介吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.78,0:19:35.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊介今天的幸運數字是…9
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.87,0:19:37.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要鬧了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.75,0:19:42.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只剩一次機會
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.62,0:19:44.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒時間猶豫了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.38,0:19:47.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,0 7 1 剩下的數字是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.38,0:19:55.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生日快樂 首藤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.22,0:19:57.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生日
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.22,0:19:59.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是7月14日
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.85,0:20:04.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,密碼 0 7 1 4
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.77,0:20:09.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生日？那是不能作為密碼的數字第一位
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.98,0:20:11.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有其他選擇了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.11,0:20:13.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有賭一賭了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.70,0:20:20.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 兔角同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.92,0:20:27.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾經也有過重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.59,0:20:29.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生日只差一天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.34,0:20:33.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首藤同學的重要的人的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.63,0:20:35.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和首藤同學僅差一天的15日
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.39,0:20:38.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後的數字一定不是4
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.58,0:21:07.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兔角同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.34,0:21:12.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一之瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.64,0:21:23.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那個人的生日呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.35,0:21:29.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一之瀨晴 你竟然注意到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.77,0:21:30.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首藤同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.69,0:21:35.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.90,0:21:38.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首藤同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.12,0:21:41.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你其實有多大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.66,0:21:45.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰知道呢 我已經忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.81,0:23:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.67,0:23:27.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天國之門與地獄之門
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.63,0:23:30.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在門的前面站著兩個守門人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.18,0:23:33.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個只說實話 另一個只說謊話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.64,0:23:35.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,機會只有一次
